citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:45am on
20-Sep-18.
Arrived at facility but owner was not present. During a telephone call, she stated that she was unable to facilitate an
inspection on this date.
